tion":{"start":{"line":1,"column":23,"offset":22},"end":{"line":1,"column":521,"offset":520},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":23,"offset":22},"end":{"line":1,"column":521,"offset":520},"indent":[]}},{"type":"text","value":") ，有一些感触，Excel很土？微服务很潮？","position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":521,"offset":520},"end":{"line":1,"column":544,"offset":543},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":1,"column":544,"offset":543},"indent":[]}},{"type":"blockquote","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"你知道GFS和Map/Reduce，但是你知道它们是为了解决什么问题的吗？是为了计算、存储、索引所有的网页（那个时候大概有8000万）。你知道SOA，但是你知道亚马逊什么时候上的SOA吗？那时候亚马逊已经有7800名雇员，年营业额超过30亿美元了。你只知道数据库集群、NoSQL，但是你知道吗？Stack Exchange在2016年，面对2亿的日访问量，只有4台SQLServer……","position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":3,"offset":546},"end":{"line":2,"column":196,"offset":739},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":3,"offset":546},"end":{"line":2,"column":196,"offset":739},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":1,"offset":544},"end":{"line":2,"column":196,"offset":739},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"我听到过这样的声音，“公司用的技术太落后了，现在用某某新技术可能可以解决我们现在碰到的问题，但是集成不进来，这个问题没法解决了…”、“我们再在这个公司待下去就完了，我现在都不敢出去找工作，感觉自己什么都不会了…”、“我们还在用SQLServer，简直无语了…”","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":741},"end":{"line":4,"column":137,"offset":877},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":741},"end":{"line":4,"column":137,"offset":877},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"类似这样的话，我也说过，但是仔细想想，技术能力的提升，真的就要去学习最新最优的高大上的技术吗？如果我们不知道为什么要使用它，那我们能把它的作用发挥到多少呢？记得我的老师说过一句话，“程序员的一生都在不断的发现问题、解决问题。”其实我们就是在各种问题、各种麻烦中成长，说白了就是要切合实际的使用技术，学以致用。","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1,"offset":879},"end":{"line":6,"column":155,"offset":1033},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1,"offset":879},"end":{"line":6,"column":155,"offset":1033},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"我的上司也是程序员出生，他毕业进公司的时候还不大流行ORM框架，用jsp+jdbc写了好几个网站项目，写statement写到想吐，后来hibernate成了他的大爱，“写hibernate的人肯定也是写jdbc写到想吐的人，他们实现了我想要的工具，我学习hibernate的过程非常轻松。”","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1,"offset":1035},"end":{"line":8,"column":147,"offset":1181},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1,"offset":1035},"end":{"line":8,"column":147,"offset":1181},"indent":[]}},{"type":"blockquote","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"linkReference","identifier":"余晟以为","referenceType":"shortcut","children":[{"type":"text","value":"余晟以为","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":3,"offset":1186},"end":{"line":11,"column":7,"offset":1190},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":2,"offset":1185},"end":{"line":11,"column":8,"offset":1191},"indent":[]}},{"type":"text","value":"(","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":8,"offset":1191},"end":{"line":11,"column":9,"offset":1192},"indent":[]}},{"type":"link","title":null,"url":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MDMwOTcwMg==&mid=2650004876&idx=1&sn=bc4df15cace45d179b901b50dcf3b8ea&chksm=8739bfa5b04e36b3c95341f740b5e1ebfbcf311495eacdcf051357dd8e9029d90ae3359e2beb&mpshare=1&scene=1&srcid=0628S9yRn3eMX8JwUYKWhpJA&key=dd608d91fd702d6496c006a68fd69e39f774135c054a342d5a4841017e6ae4a3a06ef5a1afd4ea6980a7327880db71213a3a2f08bb0d537e9c92fbd3e09d3c4c8e87cd0d67a641e23456ccd342ae298f&ascene=0&uin=MTIwODAwNzAyMA%3D%3D&devicetype=iMac+MacBookPro12%2C1+OSX+OSX+10.12.5+build(16F73)：微服务很新，微服务很潮，微服务很高大上。我在面试架构师的时候，很多候选人说到微服务，都可以侃侃而谈，各种新鲜的名词、概念、框架止不住地蹦出来，却没法回答几个问题：为什么微服务会崛起？什么时候应当实行微服务？实行微服务要注意什么？甚至，连微服务与SOA的关系是什么都搞不清楚。","children":[{"type":"text","value":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MDMwOTcwMg==&mid=2650004876&idx=1&sn=bc4df15cace45d179b901b50dcf3b8ea&chksm=8739bfa5b04e36b3c95341f740b5e1ebfbcf311495eacdcf051357dd8e9029d90ae3359e2beb&mpshare=1&scene=1&srcid=0628S9yRn3eMX8JwUYKWhpJA&key=dd608d91fd702d6496c006a68fd69e39f774135c054a342d5a4841017e6ae4a3a06ef5a1afd4ea6980a7327880db71213a3a2f08bb0d537e9c92fbd3e09d3c4c8e87cd0d67a641e23456ccd342ae298f&ascene=0&uin=MTIwODAwNzAyMA%3D%3D&devicetype=iMac+MacBookPro12%2C1+OSX+OSX+10.12.5+build(16F73)：微服务很新，微服务很潮，微服务很高大上。我在面试架构师的时候，很多候选人说到微服务，都可以侃侃而谈，各种新鲜的名词、概念、框架止不住地蹦出来，却没法回答几个问题：为什么微服务会崛起？什么时候应当实行微服务？实行微服务要注意什么？甚至，连微服务与SOA的关系是什么都搞不清楚。","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":9,"offset":1192},"end":{"line":11,"column":646,"offset":1829},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":9,"offset":1192},"end":{"line":11,"column":646,"offset":1829},"indent":[]}},{"type":"text","value":"\n要知道，架构师并不是“框架和解决方案推广落地人员”，他是需要做决策的，软件开发中，架构决策对系统的影响往往是至关重要的，一旦出现问题，后果可能相当严重。所以，合格的架构师对于微服务，不但需要了解现成的方案和概念，更应该真正的问题是什么，决策的依据是什么，然后才能知道，自己的决策是否合理","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":646,"offset":1829},"end":{"line":12,"column":145,"offset":1974},"indent":[2]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":2,"offset":1185},"end":{"line":12,"column":145,"offset":1974},"indent":[2]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1,"offset":1184},"end":{"line":12,"column":145,"offset":1974},"indent":[1]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":12,"column":145,"offset":1974}}}}